title: Looking for a serious ranked team!
body:
LF a serious rank team plat + preferred.
Main support and jungle, can fill the rest.
Can play monday to friday 5pm onwards sydney/melbourne time.
Anything just add me.

replies.body: added you ingame, im making a ranked team (made high plat last season before leaving), hopefully will make it again, ill be on around 5ish so add me and we can talk about it :P
